{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>REFLEX BASED DECISION MAKING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/Gif_04.gif?t=1739790897\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blend <strong>gunplay</strong>, and <strong>hand-to-hand combat</strong>, to eliminate waves of enemies with brutal efficiency. Master the art of the fight. Every little decision matters. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/Gif_05-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1739790897\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><br><strong>INTENSE BOSS DUELS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/Gif_01.gif?t=1739790897\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Everything you've learned will be tested by a variety of competent  bosses. Each enemy presents a <strong>unique challenge</strong>. They're not bullet sponges; you\u2019ll need to analyze their patterns and weaknesses, coming up with creative, precise strategies to defeat them. Your arsenal is only part of the equation\u2014<strong>your mind is your deadliest weapon.</strong><br><br>Until you face the Ultimate challenger,<br><strong>YOUR OWN SHADOW</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/extras/vlcsnap-2025-02-17-18h08m16s824.png?t=1739790897\" /><strong></strong></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2181220?t=1739790897","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739790897","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181220/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739790897","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as